1
00:00:00,280 --> 00:00:02,160
You loved me, yet you gave up on me.

2
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:05,360
I gave up?

3
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:07,160
You knew where I was.

4
00:00:07,760 --> 00:00:10,160
But you didn't call,
you didn't come for me.

5
00:00:10,560 --> 00:00:12,320
You were quiet for 100 days.

6
00:00:13,120 --> 00:00:14,120
Is this love?

7
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:15,520
You didn’t give me a chance!

8
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:17,840
You ran away like a coward!

9
00:00:18,120 --> 00:00:19,960
You can’t blame me

10
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:22,880
for not chasing after the
woman who wanted to divorce me!”

11
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:24,920
Did you talk Cemal, mom?

12
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,280
Don't worry.

13
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,880
He won't tell Ateş immediately.

14
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:31,000
Don’t you know how
loyal this man is to Ateş?

15
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:33,880
Keeping quiet would be like betraying him.

16
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:37,240
Cemal doesn’t foul the plate he eats from.

17
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:40,536
As much as he feels gratitude toward
Ateş, he feels the same toward me.

18
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,680
You look beautiful.

19
00:00:42,360 --> 00:00:43,400
Thank you.

20
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:46,080
What are they doing?

21
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:48,760
What are you doing here, this late?

22
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:53,240
Mr. Ateş prepared a
romantic dinner for her.

23
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:54,760
Enough!

24
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:56,920
I’m sick of these outbursts of yours!

25
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,080
Let go of my arm.

26
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:00,320
Get a grip!

27
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,080
He was perfectly happy without you.

28
00:01:02,680 --> 00:01:04,720
He’s counting the days
until he’s rid of you.

29
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:07,640
Why do you care about
our marriage this much?

30
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,760
We love each other!

31
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:14,360
You should accept that fact already.

32
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,680
You, again?

33
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:22,720
What kind of person
are you? you never learn!

34
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,440
So you love Ateş…

35
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,360
and you don’t intend to divorce him.

36
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,080
Aslı,

37
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,400
Put the knife down.

38
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,840
I warned you so many times,

